15 WHEREAS, they provide an opportunity for students not only to gain confidence and
16 knowledge through competition but also to become more motivated in becoming better
17 students and more productive citizens, which in turn develops school and community leaders.
18 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
19 recognize February 2025 as Career and Technical Education Month and February 5, 2025,
20 as Georgia Career and Technical Student Organizations Day at the state capitol.
21 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
22 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the Georgia
23 Department of Education.
